<div style="margin-left:20%;padding:1px 16px;">

<p>I'm an Assistant Professor of phonology at the Rutgers <a href="http://ling.rutgers.edu">Department of Linguistics</a>. I'm interested in mathematical and computational approaches to phonology, phonological representation, and phonological learning.</p>

<p>I'm new here and so this website is under construction.</p>

<p>For the basics, here are my <a href="files/cv.pdf">CV</a> and <a href="files/jardine2016dissertation.pdf">dissertation</a>. <a href="http://udel.edu/~ajardine">My old website</a> at the University of Delaware has some more information.</p>

<p>You can get in touch with me at <a href="mailto:adam.jardine@rutgers.edu">adam.jardine@rutgers.edu</a>.</p>

